      exact mem_nhdsWithin_iff_exists_mem_nhds_inter.2 ‚ü®w, w_open.mem_nhds q‚ÇÄw, Subset.rfl‚ü©
    filter_upwards [this]
    rintro ‚ü®p, x‚ü© hpx
